snippet: Mr. Akens had a Top 10 hit in 1965 with “The Birds and the Bees.”
abstract: Jewel Akens, singer of The Birds and the Bees, No 3 on the Billboard Hot 100 in 1965, dies at age 79.
lead_paragraph: Mr. Akens had a Top 10 hit in 1965 with “The Birds and the Bees.”
